```mermaid
flowchart TD
    Start([Start]) --> Init["pick a number between 1-100"]
    Init --> Input["tell the user to guess"]
    Input --> Validate["see if they guessed correctly (a number thats in range)"]
    Validate -- "invalid input" --> Error["show error message"]
    Error --> Input
    Validate -- "Valid input" --> Compare["Compare guess to the target number"]
    Compare -- "Guess too high" --> High["Inform user the guess is too high"]
    High --> Input
    Compare -- "Guess too low" --> Low["Inform user the guess is too low"]
    Low --> Input
    Compare -- "Correct guess" --> Correct["Congratulate the user"]
    Correct --> End([End])
```
